description: Discover this much sought-after schoolhouse condominium, a secure investment/home with two deeded parking spaces. This dramatic two-bedroom, one-bath unit with soaring ceilings and oversized windows is well-located in the heart of South Boston within steps to the Broadway shops, all bus lines, M Street beach, and minutes to the Seaport Area. The open living/dining room off the working kitchen leads to a private balcony and the parking area. Other features include refinished hardwood floors, two spacious bedrooms, and a deeded storage unit (only 1 of 2). The condo fee includes hot water...Did I mention the two deeded spaces? No space markers are needed here in this professionally managed building!
